(50, 1, '2020-08-17 23:16:09', '2020-08-17 23:16:09', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The leather in the upper feels comfortable while stitched overlays and exposed needlework adds to the throwback look.</li>\r\n 	<li>The vintage treatment on the midsole combines with heritage styling for an old-school look and feel.</li>\r\n 	<li>The vulcanized construction fuses the outsole to the midsole for a streamlined look.</li>\r\n 	<li>The exposed foam on the tongue provides a retro look and adds a super soft feel.</li>\r\n 	<li>The non-marking, solid-rubber sole has a heritage herringbone pattern for excellent traction and durability.</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Ash Green</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: CZ4609-300</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Blazer \'77 Vintage', '<b class=\"headline-5\">VINTAGE HOOPS STYLE.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe Nike Blazer \'77 Vintage harnesses the old-school look of Nike b-ball with a vintage midsole finish, making it look like you\'ve been saving them for years. Its luscious suede, retro Swoosh and padded collar make it a modern staple while the ultra-clean colors add a crisp look that completes any outfit.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Ash Green</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: CZ4609-300</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-blazer-77-vintage', '', '', '2020-08-18 19:18:32', '2020-08-18 19:18:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=50', 0, 'product', '', 0),
