(82, 1, '2020-08-18 00:22:06', '2020-08-18 00:22:06', '<b class=\"headline-5\">All About Air</b>\r\n\r\nThe Max Air unit means you can see the Air from 270 degrees around. Mix in soft foam for cushioning that never stops.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Breathable Fit</b>\r\n\r\nTextile material provides a structured fit and ventilation where you need it most.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Secure Feel</b>\r\n\r\nThe structured heel clip delivers stability when you\'re on the go.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Pull tab</li>\r\n 	<li>Rubber sole</li>\r\n 	<li>Padded collar</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Barely Rose/Atomic Pink</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: DC1864-600</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Air Max 272', '<b class=\"headline-5\">BOLD AIR. LIFTED FEEL.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nElevate your sneaker game to a bigger and bolder level in the Nike Air Max 272. A supersized heel Air unit with a breathable upper delivers a lightweight, lifted ride.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul class=\"description-preview__features pt8-sm pb6-sm ncss-list-ul\">\r\n 	<li class=\"description-preview__color-description ncss-li\">Shown: Barely Rose/Atomic Pink</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"description-preview__style-color ncss-li\">Style: DC1864-600</li>\r\n</ul>', 'trash', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-air-max-272__trashed', '', '', '2020-08-18 00:25:55', '2020-08-18 00:25:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=82', 0, 'product', '', 0),
