(88, 1, '2020-08-18 00:34:47', '2020-08-18 00:34:47', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Targeted Breathability</b>\r\n\r\n\"Just Do It.\" perforations on upper enhance breathability in forefoot and arch.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Complete Cushioning</b>\r\n\r\nFull-length Zoom Air unit provides a smooth, responsive ride. Foam in the midsole provides firm yet responsive cushioning.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Fit For Fast</b>\r\n\r\nExposed Flywire cables in the midfoot promote a snug fit at higher speeds. Its slimmer design reduces bulk for a comfortable, conforming fit.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Perforations on the upper enhance breathability in forefoot and arch.</li>\r\n 	<li>High-resiliency sockliner adapts to the contour of your foot for support.</li>\r\n 	<li>Waffle pistons on outsole help absorb impact and provide multi-surface traction.</li>\r\n 	<li>Heel collar tapers around the Achilles tendon for added comfort.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tongue weight reduced from the Pegasus 35</li>\r\n 	<li>Weight: 8.18oz (Women\'s size 8)</li>\r\n 	<li>Offset: 9.45mm (Forefoot: 14.80mm, Heel: 24.25mm)</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Football Grey/Hydrogen Blue/Aurora Green/White</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: BQ5403-005</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 36 Premium', '<b class=\"headline-5\">AN ICON GETS SLIMMER AND COOLER.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 36 Premium returns with more cooling perforations and fabric in the upper that helps target breathability across high-heat areas. Slimmer heel collar and tongue reduces bulk, while exposed Flywire cables give you a snug fit at higher speeds.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Football Grey/Hydrogen Blue/Aurora Green/White</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: BQ5403-005</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-air-zoom-pegasus-36-premium', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:06:53', '2020-0