(108, 1, '2020-08-18 00:54:25', '2020-08-18 00:54:25', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Breathable fabric and synthetic upper is engineered for durability and support.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nike React technology and Zoom Air unit give you an extremely smooth ride.</li>\r\n 	<li>Foam pods inside the collar hug the back of your foot for a secure feel.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dynamic Fit technology integrates Flywire cables with laces for a supportive feel in the midfoot.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Weight: 8.78oz (Women\'s size 8)</li>\r\n 	<li>Offset: 10mm (Forefoot: 12mm, Heel: 22mm)</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/Thunder Grey/White</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: AH7858-011</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Air Zoom Vomero 14', '<b class=\"headline-5\">BREAKTHROUGH RESPONSIVENESS.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe Nike Air Zoom Vomero 14 takes responsive cushioning to the next level. The full-length Zoom Air unit works with Nike React cushioning to deliver a super snappy, smooth ride. Up top, the sleek design is engineered to support your stride.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/Thunder Grey/White</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: AH7858-011</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-air-zoom-vomero-14', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:04:50', '2020-08-18 04:04:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=108', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(109, 1, '2020-08-18 00:50:30', '2020-08-18 00:50:30', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Spring With Your Step</b>\n\nNike React foam at the midsole is lightweight, springy and durable. More foam means better cushioning without the bulk. A Zoom Air unit at the forefoot is twice as large as previous versions, delivering more bounce with every step. It\'s top-loaded to be closer to your foot for better responsiveness.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Evolved Fit</b>\n\nA midfoot band adapts to the size of your foot, keeping you comfortable and secure with every step.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Ready for Speed</b>\n\nA translucent upper has the look of speed and is made to help your foot while you run. Mesh details throughout promote ventilation.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Product Details</strong>\n<ul class=\"description-preview__features pt8-sm pb6-sm ncss-list-ul\">\n 	<li class=\"description-preview__color-description ncss-li\">Shown: White/Black/Flash Crimson/Multi-Color</li>\n 	<li class=\"description-preview__style-color ncss-li\">Style: CZ7864-100</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 37', '<p><b class=\"headline-5\">RUN IN COLOR.</b></p><p><br></p><p>Inspired by the vibrant energy and sights that take place during a color run, the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 37 brings those electrifying feels to your feet. Run wild in the same fit and feel that you\'ve always loved about the Peg, plus an all-new forefoot cushioning unit and foam for optimal responsiveness.</p><p><br></p><ul class=\"description-preview__features pt8-sm pb6-sm ncss-list-ul\"><li class=\"description-preview__color-description ncss-li\">Shown: White/Black/Flash Crimson/Multi-Color</li><li class=\"description-preview__style-color ncss-li\">Style: CZ7864-100</li></ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '102-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 00:50:30', '2020-08-18 00:50:30', '', 102, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/102-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
