(115, 1, '2020-08-18 01:01:26', '2020-08-18 01:01:26', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>2 Zoom Air units give a responsive, stable feeling underfoot.</li>\r\n 	<li>Engineered mesh and synthetic upper provides supportive structure and breathability.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sleek, sculpted profile creates a fast look and feel.</li>\r\n 	<li>Partial bootie wraps the foot for a secure, snug fit.</li>\r\n 	<li>Heel foam sweeps away from the Achilles tendon for optimal comfort.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lightweight Cushlon foam delivers soft and springy midsole cushioning.</li>\r\n 	<li>Modified Waffle tread on the medial side gives you excellent traction.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rubber crash rail on the lateral outsole acts as a cushioning device, while a crash pad enhances durability in the high-wear zone.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Weight: 7.92oz (Women\'s size 8)</li>\r\n 	<li>Offset: 10mm (Forefoot: 13.5mm, Heel: 23.5mm)</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/Photon Dust/Valerian Blue/Vivid Purple</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: AQ8228-006</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Air Zoom Winflo 6', '<b class=\"headline-5\">THE WAY SPEEDY LOOKS NOW.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn a fluid design that speaks the language of fast, the Nike Air Zoom Winflo 6 has less bulk and a more sculpted profile than previous versions. It has 2 Zoom Air units for targeted responsiveness in the forefoot and heel. Up top, engineered mesh optimizes breathability.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/Photon Dust/Valerian Blue/Vivid Purple</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: AQ8228-006</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-air-zoom-winflo-6', '', '', '2020-08-18 21:59:30', '2020-08-18 21:59:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=115', 0, 'product', '', 0),
