(139, 1, '2020-08-18 01:25:24', '2020-08-18 01:25:24', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Second-Skin Fit</b>\r\n\r\nA comfortable lining and Dynamic Fit collar work together and wrap your foot to feel like a second skin.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Textured for Touch</b>\r\n\r\nSoft synthetic material is textured from heel to toe to give you the touch you need for creativity at high speeds.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Explosive Traction</b>\r\n\r\nForefoot plate provides explosive traction on artificial-grass surfaces.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dynamic Fit collar</li>\r\n 	<li>Sockliner for lightweight cushioning</li>\r\n 	<li>Higher plate overlap on the toe for durability</li>\r\n 	<li>Best for use on outdoor synthetic fields</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: White/Photon Dust/Hyper Jade/Flash Crimson</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: BQ5424-163</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Mercurial Superfly 7 Academy AG', '<b class=\"headline-5\">FINESSED FOR SPEED.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBuilding on the forefoot plate innovation of the 6, the Nike Mercurial Superfly 7 Academy Cleat provides explosive traction on artificial-grass surfaces.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: White/Photon Dust/Hyper Jade/Flash Crimson</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: BQ5424-163</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-mercurial-superfly-7-academy-ag', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:02:50', '2020-08-18 04:02:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=139', 0, 'product', '', 0),
