(147, 1, '2020-08-18 01:30:58', '2020-08-18 01:30:58', '<b class=\"headline-5\">High-Tenacity Fit</b>\r\n\r\n360-degree Flyknit construction wraps your foot for a second-skin fit. New high-tenacity yarn and a 1-piece lining create a streamlined, secure feel on the field.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">All-Weather Touch</b>\r\n\r\nA new ultra-thin NIKESKIN overlay gets you closer to the ball for a precise touch at high speeds. All Conditions Control (ACC) technology means you get reliable touch in wet and dry conditions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Explosive Acceleration</b>\r\n\r\nThe lightweight forefoot plate features a Nike Aerotrak zone with microgrooves. The angular studs combine with a new, stiffer plate for explosive acceleration with every step.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dynamic Fit collar</li>\r\n 	<li>Insole with NikeGrip technology</li>\r\n 	<li>Best for use on synthetic fields</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/Dark Smoke Grey/Black</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: AT7892-060</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Mercurial Superfly 7 Elite AG-PRO', '<b class=\"headline-5\">FINESSED FOR SPEED.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBuilding on the 360-degree Flyknit innovation of the 6, the Nike Mercurial Superfly 7 Elite AG-PRO adds a Nike Aerotrak zone to the forefoot and a slightly stiffer plate to help supercharge traction.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/Dark Smoke Grey/Black</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: AT7892-060</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-mercurial-superfly-7-elite-ag-pro', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:02:46', '2020-08-18 04:02:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=147', 0, 'product', '', 0),
