(163, 1, '2020-08-18 01:37:16', '2020-08-18 01:37:16', '<b class=\"headline-5\">High-Tenacity Fit</b>\n\n360-degree Flyknit construction wraps your foot for a second-skin fit. New high-tenacity yarn and a 1-piece lining create a snug, secure feel on the field.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">All-Weather Touch</b>\n\nA new ultra-thin NIKESKIN overlay gets you closer to the ball for a precise touch. The All Conditions Control (ACC) finish means you get reliable contact in wet and dry conditions.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Explosive Acceleration</b>\n\nThe lightweight forefoot plate features a Nike Aerotrak zone with micro grooves. The angular studs combine with a new stiffer chassis for explosive acceleration with every step.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Insole with NikeGrip technology</li>\n 	<li>Best for use on slightly wet short-grass fields</li>\n 	<li>Shown: White/Racer Blue/Volt/Black</li>\n 	<li>Style: AT7898-104</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Mercurial Vapor 13 Elite Neymar Jr. FG', '<b class=\"headline-5\">FINESSED FOR SPEED. FINISHED FOR NEYMAR JR.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nBuilding on the 360 innovation of the 12, the Nike Mercurial Vapor 13 Elite Neymar Jr. FG adds a Nike Aerotrak zone to the forefoot and a slightly stiffer chassis to help supercharge traction. Inside, an insole with NikeGrip technology provides maximum interior traction underfoot and lightweight cushioning.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: White/Racer Blue/Volt/Black</li>\n 	<li>Style: AT7898-104</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '155-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 01:37:16', '2020-08-18 01:37:16', '', 155, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/155-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(164, 1, '2020-08-18 01:44:47', '2020-08-18 01:44:47', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Full-Length, Close-to-Foot Cushioning</b>\r\n\r\nA full-length Nike Air Zoom cushion is stitched directly to the upper. It follows the shape of your foot to give an ultra-responsive sensation and a smooth heel-to-toe transition.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Double-Stacked Zoom Air</b>\r\n\r\nA second Zoom Air unit is stacked underneath the full-length Nike Air Zoom cushion in the forefoot. It helps enable movements and energy return.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Broken-In Comfort</b>\r\n\r\nLightweight and flexible, the soft upper is constructed from minimal materials for a broken-in feel. This makes it court-ready right out of the box.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Product Detais</strong>\r\n<ul class=\"description-preview__features pt8-sm pb6-sm ncss-list-ul\">\r\n 	<li class=\"description-preview__color-description ncss-li\">Shown: White/Baltic Blue/Summit White/Metallic Gold</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"description-preview__style-color ncss-li\">Style: DA0895-102</li>\r\n</ul>', 'KD13', '<b class=\"headline-5\">BUILT TO BE CLUTCH.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIn the games crucial moments, KD thrives. He makes defenders fear his unstoppable moves and shuts down opponents with his defensive prowess. The KD13 helps him play at an elite level with full-length Nike Air Zoom cushioning. An extra forefoot Zoom Air unit provides amazing energy return for every moveall game long.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul class=\"description-preview__features pt8-sm pb6-sm ncss-list-ul\">\r\n 	<li class=\"description-preview__color-description ncss-li\">Shown: White/Baltic Blue/Summit White/Metallic Gold</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"description-preview__style-color ncss-li\">Style: DA0895-102</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'kd13', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:02:37', '2020-08-18 04:02:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=164', 0, 'product', '', 0),
