(170, 1, '2020-08-18 01:49:07', '2020-08-18 01:49:07', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Ready Responsiveness</b>\r\n\r\nNike Zoom Air cushioning under the ball of your foot helps deliver a burst of responsive energy generated by your own force.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Secure, Stable Fit</b>\r\n\r\nThe laces feed through webbing loops to help the shoe fit securely and keep you stable over the midsole.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Lightweight Agility</b>\r\n\r\nLow-top design is sleek and lightweight, providing support without sacrificing agility.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Rep Mamba</b>\r\n\r\nA Kobe sheath logo is featured on the tongue, back of the heel and outsole. A snakeskin-inspired traction pattern helps keep you in control.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">More Benefits</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The Swoosh design is textured with a scale pattern that extends up the sides.</li>\r\n 	<li>Minimally structured upper provides a lightweight, agile feel.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rubber extends along the sides to provide stability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Small TPU heel clip behind Achilles</li>\r\n 	<li>Kobe storytelling details</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/University Gold/University Red</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: CK2087-002</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Mamba Fury', '<b class=\"headline-5\">KOBE\'S MENTALITY REBORN.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNamed for a raw emotion that defined Kobe Bryant\'s legendary game, the Mamba Fury is sleek and stripped down for a fast, lightweight look and feel. Its low-profile responsiveness and aggressive traction are hallmarks of Kobe\'s shoes. The low-cut collar allows players the freedom to cut hard while maintaining speed.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/University Gold/University Red</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: CK2087-002</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mamba-fury', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:02:26', '2020-08-18 04:02:26', '',