(176, 1, '2020-08-18 01:55:24', '2020-08-18 01:55:24', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Quick, Easy On and Off</b>\r\n\r\nWith a fold-down heel and 2 pull loops, the collar opens wide for quick, easy entry. Pulling up on the strap tightens the Flywire cables on both sides of the heel and over the top.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Built For Basketball</b>\r\n\r\nA soft, resilient foam midsole provides cushioning and support. Durable rubber on the outsole has a circular tread pattern. It wraps up the inside of the forefoot, providing traction when running and cutting.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">More Benefits</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Padded, contoured collar provides a comfortable fit around the ankle.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rubber outsole with circular traction pattern and pivot point.</li>\r\n 	<li>Toe skin helps resist abrasion.</li>\r\n 	<li>Contoured graphics make the shoe look fast.</li>\r\n 	<li>Design is made for wider feet.</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/White</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: CV3452-001</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Precision 4 FlyEase', '<b class=\"headline-5\">UNLIMITED GAME.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf you\'re a basketball player who prefers the quickness and ease of a laceless shoe, check out the Nike Precision 4 FlyEase. The heel folds back to make a wide entry to slide in your foot. Once inside, pull up on the strap to tighten the Flywire cables for a secure fit.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: Black/White</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: CV3452-001</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-precision-4-flyease', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:02:18', '2020-08-18 04:02:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=176', 0, 'product', '', 0),
