(206, 1, '2020-08-18 03:28:09', '2020-08-18 03:28:09', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Strategic Stability</b>\r\n\r\nA low, flat, wide heel now features a removable Hyperlift insert that adds offset to help improve stability for squats, wall balls and thrusters.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Zoned Durability</b>\r\n\r\nA rubber sidewall wraps up the midfoot for abrasion-resistant grip for rope climbs. The small protrusion on the back is designed to help you get up and down the wall faster during handstands.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Diverse Cushioning</b>\r\n\r\nGo from heavy lifts to burpees with tuned cushioning thats firm in back and dynamic in front.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Tough Traction</b>\r\n\r\nA rubber sole grips the floor for moves like agility drills and sled pushes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">More Benefits</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Flywire cables link with the laces and hug the midfoot to help hold your foot down as you move.</li>\r\n 	<li>3D print around the toe creates durability.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Foam midsole</li>\r\n 	<li>Shown: White/Hyper Crimson/Pink/Psychic Blue</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: CJ0818-146</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Nike Metcon 5 Premium', '<b class=\"headline-5\">BUILT FOR STRENGTH AND SPEED.</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe Nike Metcon 5 Premium arms you with stability for heavy lifting and traction for sprints during high-impact training. It combines breathability and durability to be your secret weapon in the gym.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shown: White/Hyper Crimson/Pink/Psychic Blue</li>\r\n 	<li>Style: CJ0818-146</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nike-metcon-5-premium', '', '', '2020-08-18 03:59:56', '2020-08-18 03:59:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/divi/?post_type=product&#038;p=206', 0, 'product', '', 0),
