(219, 1, '2020-08-18 21:07:30', '2020-08-18 21:07:30', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Strategic Stability</b>\n\nA low, flat and wide heel now features a removable Hyperlift insert that adds offset to help improve stability for squats, wall balls and thrusters.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Zoned Durability</b>\n\nTextured print on the top of the shoe adds lightweight durability where it\'s needed.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Enhanced Grip</b>\n\nDirectional traction on the outsole wraps up the side of the shoe for grip when climbing a rope and speed when sliding down.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Diverse Cushioning</b>\n\nFoam is firmer under the heel for a secure feel, and softer in the forefoot to cushion high-impact moves.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">More Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Hyperlift insert is compatible with all prior versions of the Metcon.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Metcon logo on tongue</li>\n 	<li>Swoosh design on heel</li>\n 	<li>Shown: Black/Light Current Blue/Desert Sand</li>\n 	<li>Style: AQ1189-040</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Metcon 5', '<b class=\"headline-5\">OUR MOST STABLE AND DURABLE METCON.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe Nike Metcon 5 is our most tuned Metcon yet. This means specific stability for heavy lifting, traction made for speed, and durability where you need it. It even includes a Hyperlift insert that\'s compatible with all prior versions of the Metcon. Meet your secret weapon for weight lifting and high-impact training.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: Black/Light Current Blue/Desert Sand</li>\n 	<li>Style: AQ1189-040</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '200-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 21:07:30', '2020-08-18 21:07:30', '', 200, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/200-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(220, 1, '2020-08-18 04:04:52', '2020-08-18 04:04:52', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Mesh Breathability</b>\n\nThe lofted mesh and synthetic upper is lighter than its predecessor, and the translucent material makes it look as breathable as it feels.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Comfortable for Distance</b>\n\nA partial inner sleeve from toe to midfoot, combined with a more traditional shape from midfoot to heel is designed to help you train faster, longer.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Absorbs Impact</b>\n\nThe rubber outsole helps absorb impact and provide multi-surface traction.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">More Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>An ultralight Nike ZoomX midsole delivers Nike Running\'s greatest energy return yet.</li>\n 	<li>The engineered heel collar tapers away from foot for comfort around your Achilles tendon.</li>\n 	<li>An angled heel optimizes initial touchdown and provides a smooth transition.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Weight: 8.16 oz. (men\'s size 10)</li>\n 	<li>Offset: 8mm (16mm forefoot, 24mm heel)</li>\n 	<li>Exaggerated Swoosh design extends over the midsole as an emblem of Nike ZoomX</li>\n 	<li>Shown: White/Blue Void/Football Grey/Photo Blue</li>\n 	<li>Style: AT2863-100</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo 2', '<b class=\"headline-5\">A TURBOCHARGED TRAINER THAT\'S LIGHTER AND SLEEKER.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe Nike Zoom Pegasus Turbo 2 is updated with a featherlight upper, while innovative foam brings revolutionary responsiveness to your long distance training.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: White/Blue Void/Football Grey/Photo Blue</li>\n 	<li>Style: AT2863-100</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '133-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:04:52', '2020-08-18 04:04:52', '', 133, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/133-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(221, 1, '2020-08-18 04:05:02', '2020-08-18 04:05:02', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Breathable Lockdown</b>\n\nA heel clip and midfoot webbing helps keep your foot secure. Open-hole mesh at the toe increases airflow to keep you cool.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Higher Heights</b>\n\nFoam cushioning delivers a soft underfoot feel. A higher stack height gives you extra plush cushioning, so you can run in comfort.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Traction Made to Run</b>\n\nA rubber outsole delivers durable traction thatll keep you focused on your run.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">More Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Traditional lacing and tongue for easy on and off.</li>\n 	<li>Toe bumper provides abrasion resistance.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Synthetic leather and textile materials in upper</li>\n 	<li>Offset: 10mm (Forefoot: 11.5, Heel: 21.5mm)</li>\n 	<li>Shown: Black/White/University Red</li>\n 	<li>Style: CK6268-002</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Run All Day 2', '<b class=\"headline-5\">STEADY, LIGHTWEIGHT SUPPORT.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nMade for the casual runner, the Nike Run All Day 2 is all about support. Underfoot traction helps keep you steady, no matter how many miles you put in.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: Black/White/University Red</li>\n 	<li>Style: CK6268-002</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:05:02', '2020-08-18 04:05:02', '', 127, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/127-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(222, 1, '2020-08-18 04:06:17', '2020-08-18 04:06:17', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Spring With Your Step</b>\n\nNike React foam at the midsole is lightweight, springy and durable. An Air Zoom unit at the forefoot is twice as large as previous versions and is positioned closer to your foot, delivering more bounce with every step.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">A Quick, Easy Way to Start Your Run</b>\n\nZippered entry makes it easy to quickly get on and off. No-tie lacing secures the fit.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Extra Durable</b>\n\nA durable rubber outsole and a reinforced toe help resist abrasion.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Ready for Speed</b>\n\nA translucent upper has the look of speed and is made to help your foot while you run. Mesh details throughout promote ventilation.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">More Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>The tensioning cord feeds through midfoot bands that help secure the fit while you run.</li>\n 	<li>The Pegasus 37 is specifically tuned for women, with a PSI that delivers just the right cushioning for your run.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>4E design for wide feet</li>\n 	<li>Shown: White/Hyper Violet/Spruce Aura/Flash Crimson</li>\n 	<li>Style: CV1769-100</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 37 FlyEase', '<b class=\"headline-5\">RELIABLE SPEED FOR ALL ATHLETES.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n37 years and millions of miles later, the legend lives on in the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 37 FlyEase. Our most trusted running shoe flies into the future with Zoom Air specially tuned to your needs, and a FlyEase entry system that gets you in quickly and easily.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: White/Hyper Violet/Spruce Aura/Flash Crimson</li>\n 	<li>Style: CV1769-100</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '94-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:06:17', '2020-08-18 04:06:17', '', 94, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/94-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(223, 1, '2020-08-18 04:06:24', '2020-08-18 04:06:24', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Targeted Breathability</b>\n\n\"Just Do It.\" perforations on upper enhance breathability in forefoot and arch.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Complete Cushioning</b>\n\nFull-length Zoom Air unit provides a smooth, responsive ride. Foam in the midsole provides firm yet responsive cushioning.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Fit For Fast</b>\n\nExposed Flywire cables in the midfoot promote a snug fit at higher speeds. Its slimmer design reduces bulk for a comfortable, conforming fit.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Perforations on the upper enhance breathability in forefoot and arch.</li>\n 	<li>High-resiliency sockliner adapts to the contour of your foot for support.</li>\n 	<li>Waffle pistons on outsole help absorb impact and provide multi-surface traction.</li>\n 	<li>Heel collar tapers around the Achilles tendon for added comfort.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Tongue weight reduced from the Pegasus 35</li>\n 	<li>Weight: 8.18oz (Women\'s size 8)</li>\n 	<li>Offset: 9.45mm (Forefoot: 14.80mm, Heel: 24.25mm)</li>\n 	<li>Shown: Football Grey/Hydrogen Blue/Aurora Green/White</li>\n 	<li>Style: BQ5403-005</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 36 Premium', '<b class=\"headline-5\">AN ICON GETS SLIMMER AND COOLER.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 36 Premium returns with more cooling perforations and fabric in the upper that helps target breathability across high-heat areas. Slimmer heel collar and tongue reduces bulk, while exposed Flywire cables give you a snug fit at higher speeds.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: Football Grey/Hydrogen Blue/Aurora Green/White</li>\n 	<li>Style: BQ5403-005</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '88-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:06:24', '2020-08-18 04:06:24', '', 88, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/88-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(224, 1, '2020-08-18 22:04:29', '2020-08-18 22:04:29', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Lightweight Design</b>\n\nThe ultralight design is inspired by marathon runners\' shoes.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">All-Day Comfort</b>\n\nA foam midsole provides soft cushioning and long-lasting comfort.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Sport Inspiration</b>\n\nFlywire cables minimize weight and maximize support.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Mesh and textile upper</li>\n 	<li>Minimal tongue for fewer layers</li>\n 	<li>Round laces</li>\n 	<li>Shown: Wolf Grey</li>\n 	<li>Style: AT4345-005</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Viale Tech Racer', '<b class=\"headline-5\">LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN. LONG-DISTANCE COMFORT.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe Nike Viale Tech Racer brings a modern, angular aesthetic to the philosophy of fast. With a design inspired by long-distance running shoes, it\'s lightweight and comfortable for all-day wear.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: Wolf Grey</li>\n 	<li>Style: AT4345-005</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '76-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 22:04:29', '2020-08-18 22:04:29', '', 76, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/76-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(225, 1, '2020-08-18 04:08:18', '2020-08-18 04:08:18', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Premium denim is durable and comfortable.</li>\n 	<li>The low-profile upper is inspired by classic tennis shoes.</li>\n 	<li>Raw edges and distinct design lines create an experimental aesthetic.</li>\n 	<li>A rubber toe cap enhances durability.</li>\n 	<li>The leather backtab mimics the classic back patch, a popular accent on jeans.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Product Details</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Cork print on sockliner</li>\n 	<li>Shown: Industrial Blue</li>\n 	<li>Style: CW6213-461</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">N354 Origins</b>\n\nPres fastest mile didnt happen in the first prototype. N354 celebrates the tool-strewn tables and torn-out pages of designers like Bill Bowerman and Tinker Hatfield, who moved Nike from good ideas to great innovation in the world of sport and culture.', 'Nike Drop-Type Premium', '<b class=\"headline-5\">IT\'S ALL IN THE DETAILS.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWell, we finally did it. We dressed the Nike Drop-Type Premium in premium denim with raw edges and accented it with double stitching at the overlays and selvage stitch on the quarter. A stitched-in logo at the tongue is just one of the discoverable details that makes the newest member of the N354 family something special.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: Industrial Blue</li>\n 	<li>Style: CW6213-461</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '71-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:08:18', '2020-08-18 04:08:18', '', 71, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/71-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(226, 1, '2020-08-18 04:08:22', '2020-08-18 04:08:22', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>A rubber waffle outsole provides traction and durability.</li>\n 	<li>A foam midsole offers lightweight cushioning for all-day comfort.</li>\n 	<li>A nylon upper with suede and synthetic leather overlays recreates the classic \'80s style.</li>\n 	<li>Shown: Blue Fury</li>\n 	<li>Style: CK2351-007</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Daybreak', '<b class=\"headline-5\">TRUE TO THE ORIGINAL.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nOriginally released in 1979, the Nike Daybreak is a blast from the past. Featuring the same rubber waffle outsole and nylon upper, it gives you true vintage style.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: Blue Fury</li>\n 	<li>Style: CK2351-007</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '68-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 04:08:22', '2020-08-18 04:08:22', '', 68, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/68-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(227, 1, '2020-08-18 19:19:08', '2020-08-18 19:19:08', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Bodega Inspiration</b>\n\nThis icon takes notes from your favorite bodega, like the grate-inspired medial panel, street art-inspired logos, cracked paint and a design on the tongue that resembles the same lines of a fruit bag.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Premium Look</b>\n\nLeather and synthetic leather add a premium look to this fresh twist on the iconic design. The low-cut silhouette offers a crisp, streamlined look.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Walking on Air</b>\n\nNike Air cushioning adds lightweight comfort.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">More Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Rubber outsole</li>\n 	<li>Shown: White</li>\n 	<li>Style: CZ8132-100</li>\n</ul>', 'Nike Air Force 1 \'07', '<b class=\"headline-5\">AN ICON GETS BODEGA-FIED.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThe Nike Air Force 1 \'07 places the precise details that characterize neighborhood corner markets onto your feet. The lined panel on the side is inspired by the shop\'s iron grates. Custom logos on the tongue top and heel piece nod to the street art that adorns a store\'s exterior. Look closer, under the logo you\'ll see cracked paint-like material, while a grid design on the tongue top resembles the lines of fruit bags.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: White</li>\n 	<li>Style: CZ8132-100</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '42-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 19:19:08', '2020-08-18 19:19:08', '', 42, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/42-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
