(282, 1, '2020-08-18 22:07:10', '2020-08-18 22:07:10', '<b class=\"headline-5\">Benefits</b>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Hand-stitched toe has a unique, raw aesthetic.</li>\n 	<li>Hairy suede upper is soft and textured.</li>\n 	<li>Leather laces are durable.</li>\n 	<li>Zoom Air unit in the sockliner delivers responsive cushioning.</li>\n 	<li>Mid-top provides a supportive fit around your ankles.</li>\n 	<li>Cork sockliner offers soft cushioning and a natural look.</li>\n 	<li>Vulcanized construction bonds the upper to the outsole for greater boardfeel, flexibility and consistent flick.</li>\n 	<li>Shown: Jade Horizon/Black/Pale Ivory/Jade Horizon</li>\n 	<li>Style: AQ7460-300</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b class=\"headline-5\">Year of Janoski</b>\n\nThe Year of Janoski celebrates the 10-year anniversary of Stefan Janoski\'s signature shoe, the Nike SB Zoom Stefan Janoski. Each season will highlight a different chapter of his life through unique materials and reimagined silhouettes. The theme of Spring 2019 is Originsa deep-dive into Janoski\'s roots and his love of handcraftsmanship.', 'Nike SB Zoom Stefan Janoski Mid Crafted', '<b class=\"headline-5\">THE GENESIS OF JANOSKI.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nKicking off the Year of Janoski, the Nike SB Zoom Stefan Janoski Mid Crafted celebrates Stefan\'s appreciation of handcraftsmanship. The minimal design, hand-stitched toe and leather laces create a raw, natural aesthetic.\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n 	<li>Shown: Jade Horizon/Black/Pale Ivory/Jade Horizon</li>\n 	<li>Style: AQ7460-300</li>\n</ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '194-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-08-18 22:07:10', '2020-08-18 22:07:10', '', 194, 'http://localhost/divi/2020/08/18/194-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
